  "texts": [
    "T5Developed and trained by Google, T5-LM is very easy to teach.",
    "During the training, T5 published a lot of content through public announcements on its website.",
    "The goal is to create a simple way to teach words that can be used in different contexts.",
    "The thing about T5 is that it knows all the hard work of creating text.",
    "Converting text from one format to another has been modified to simplify text-to-text conversion."
  ]
}